stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> ReceiveState: checkTDDRedEvidence invoked

    ReceiveState: Receive TaskState and phase
    ReceiveState --> CheckPhase

    CheckPhase: Evaluate phase value
    CheckPhase --> Exempt_NonTestImpl: phase !== test_impl
    CheckPhase --> ReadScopeFiles: phase === test_impl

    Exempt_NonTestImpl: Return passed true (not applicable)
    Exempt_NonTestImpl --> [*]

    ReadScopeFiles: Extract scopeFiles from TaskState
    ReadScopeFiles --> CheckScopeLength

    CheckScopeLength: Evaluate scopeFiles.length
    CheckScopeLength --> ExistingLogic: scopeFiles.length === 0
    CheckScopeLength --> EvalExtensions: scopeFiles.length > 0

    EvalExtensions: Check every file extension against DOC_ONLY_EXTENSIONS
    EvalExtensions --> DocOnlyExempt: all extensions in Set(.md, .mmd)
    EvalExtensions --> ExistingLogic: any extension outside Set(.md, .mmd)

    DocOnlyExempt: Return passed true with doc-only exemption evidence
    DocOnlyExempt --> [*]

    ExistingLogic: Evaluate proofLog for TDD Red evidence
    ExistingLogic --> CheckProofLog

    CheckProofLog: Search proof entries for test failure records
    CheckProofLog --> Passed: valid TDD Red evidence found
    CheckProofLog --> Failed: no TDD Red evidence found

    Passed: Return passed true with proof evidence
    Passed --> [*]

    Failed: Return passed false with missing evidence detail
    Failed --> [*]
